headline: Cresset Lures $1.8 Billion Advisory Practice From Goldman Sachs
summary: Jamie Gilbert is bringing his ultrahigh-net-worth practice to Cresset’s Atlanta office with plans to open a new location in Wyoming.

headline: ING Bank Śląski takes full control of Goldman Sachs TFI by acquiring remaining 55% stake
summary: ING Bank Śląski takes full control of Goldman Sachs TFI by acquiring remaining 55% stake ING announced today that ING Bank Śląski has reached an agreement with Goldman Sachs on the full acquisition of the Polish asset management company Goldman Sachs TFI.
